## Commit Scopes (Your Project)

**Core**: cli, playbook, schema, registry
**Analyzers**: analyzer, analyzer/trivy, analyzer/sbom, analyzer/hadolint, analyzer/skopeo, analyzer/freshness, analyzer/size, analyzer/popularity, analyzer/endoflife, analyzer/scorecarddev, analyzer/provenance
**Rendering**: report, templates
**Tooling**: ci, deps, docs

See PROJECT_SCOPES.md for details and usage guidelines.

